Search for species/organism of interest in the seach bar of Bioproject tab
Then apply filters present on left most panel by selecting the data tye of ineterest(Transcriptome), Project data(SRA), Scope (Multiple species/ Single species/ Multi isolate) and organism (plant/human/fungi/others)
To get the SRA realted data for all hits in Bioprojects, click on right most drop down menu to select SRA and click on find items below it
To download runinfo click on "send to"--> "file" --> "runinfo" --> createfile
**Done**
